Bugfix: Add rewrite base to .htaccess

In the previous core version the rewrite base was not added to the generated
.htaccess file which caused complete breakage of the web UI in combination with
the hardened .htaccess file introduced with https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/40584

https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/40696
https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/40697
